{"tid":264644,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"訛稱港隊成員掠水　羽球教練判200小時社服","createTime":"2017-05-31T03:53:28.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-31T04:16:51.000Z","uid":48093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"72f55651c85a3b45d655d6b10d97210479e619bf","tid":264644,"uid":48093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T03:53:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170531/photo/bkn-20170531114028434-0531_00822_001_01p.jpg?20170531115030\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170531%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20170531114028434-0531_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20170531115030&h=8197b099&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n海關去年偵破首宗虛報聲稱資歷提供教練服務的案件，案中一名羽毛球教練對外宣傳招生時，訛稱自己為前香港代表隊成員，曾代表香港參加亞運，並收取較一般教練貴一倍的學費，被海關「放蛇」拘捕。27歲被告梁浚豪早前承認一項「要約提供已應用虛假商品說明的服務」罪名，今在觀塘法院被判200小時社會服務令。<br />\n<br />\n裁判官今判刑時指，考慮被告過往打羽毛球比賽及經驗，背景良好，加上有悔意，故給予最後一次機會，判其200小時社會服務令，希望他好好珍惜機會。"},{"pid":"f7073ccf64330894e5c9297183cc9be6d9f3a3a3","tid":264644,"uid":37735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T03:54:52.000Z","msg":"話同過港隊成員 訓練咪算<br />\n<br />\n死無對証"},{"pid":"945a42778daf06f93a1a37834aa479160217de01","tid":264644,"uid":76117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T03:55:41.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"091d3d76e37f2865d9a296be3e8c9364e449db51","tid":264644,"uid":8858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T03:55:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><br />\n裁判官今判刑時指，<span style=\"color: red;\">考慮被告過往打羽毛球比賽及經驗，背景良好，加上有悔意</span>，故給予最後一次機會，判其200小時社會服務令，希望他好好珍惜機會。</blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\"